@RichDecibels Finding people who were curious about arguing for and against different perspectives played a big role.

It enabled me to be a skeptic to my skepticism, which then opened me up to non-naive hope. 

It also allowed me to riff on ideas that can be propped up by others.

@VividVoid_ My most liked tweet was an ironic, dystopian-cope tweet.

My tweets that attempt to grok the way forward don't nearly do as well. 

But what I realized is that there's a small group of them who like them and that's what matters more. https://t.co/eFmiNRAC7F
